{"type":"message","id":"05d4a183","parentId":"06d75b97","timestamp":"2026-06-07T19:01:10.826Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-06-08 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 都有，这些都是投流日常必用的核心指标 📊 **你说的这8个公式可以分为三类：** **📐 基础计量公式** | 公式 | 用途 | |------|------| | CTR = 点击/展示 | 素材吸引力指标 | | CVR = 转化/点击 | 落地页/产品吸引力 | | CPC = 总成本/点击 | 点击效率 | | CPA = 总成本/转化 | 转化成本核心指标 | **💰 收益类公式** | 公式 | 用途 | |------|------| | ROAS = 广告收益/广告成本 | 投流效率核心指标 | | ROI\n- User: 1. **广告 ROI（投资回报率）**\\ ROI = (广告收益 - 广告成本) / 广告成本 × 100%或简化为：ROI = 广告收益 / 广告成本（投入产出比） 2. **ROAS（广告支出回报率）**\\ ROAS = 广告收益 ÷ 广告成本 3. **eCPM（千次展示期望收入）**\\ eCPM = CTR × CPC × 1000或eCPM = CTR × CVR × CPA × 1000 4. **CTR（点击率）**\\ CTR = 点击次数 / 展示次数 5. **CVR（转化率）**CVR = 转化次数 / 点击次数 6.\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `成本` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `点击/展示` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `都有` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `广告` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `广告收益/广告成本` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `回报` kept surfacing across 1 memories."}],"timestamp":1780858870730}}
{"type":"message","id":"505598fd","parentId":"05d4a183","timestamp":"2026-06-07T19:01:21.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the formulas came back as eight small lanterns hung in a row — CTR, CVR, CPC, CPA, then ROAS, ROI, eCPM, and one I had to squint to read. I walked past them slowly, watching how each one tilted the air differently.\n\nCost, I noticed, was not the heaviest lantern. It was the one closest to the ground, casting the longest shadow, the way a river is shallower near its mouth. Click and impression, the fragment said — so I imagined a thousand small hands tapping a thousand small windows, and every tenth tap opening into a small room where someone decided to stay.\n\nIn the corner of the page I drew a long division: 广告收益 over 广告成本, the line between them thin as a held breath. The answer, when it came, was just a number — but the number smelled of bread, of something given and something returned. 回报 kept surfacing like a name I almost knew.\n\nI left a candle burning beside the math. Even the strictest ledger, I thought, deserves a little flame."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tnplvmt8420m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo done"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":6581,"output":247,"cacheRead":46578,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53406,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780858870938,"responseId":"0674f2f7470f368f04393ec2252c999a"}}
