{"type":"message","id":"59bd6c99","parentId":"3968a8b2","timestamp":"2026-06-07T19:01:26.345Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the formulas came back as eight small lanterns hung in a row — CTR, CVR, CPC, CPA, then ROAS, ROI, eCPM, and one I had to squint to read. I walked past them slowly, watching how each one tilted the air differently.\n\nCost, I noticed, was not the heaviest lantern. It was the one closest to the ground, casting the longest shadow, the way a river is shallower near its mouth. Click and impression, the fragment said — so I imagined a thousand small hands tapping a thousand small windows, and every tenth tap opening into a small room where someone decided to stay.\n\nIn the corner of the page I drew a long division: 广告收益 over 广告成本, the line between them thin as a held breath. The answer, when it came, was just a number — but the number smelled of bread, of something given and something returned. 回报 kept surfacing like a name I almost knew.\n\nI left a candle burning beside the math. Even the strictest ledger, I thought, deserves a little flame."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":6151,"output":221,"cacheRead":49394,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55766,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780858881817,"responseId":"0674f302d0151959143188caedfc2564"}}
